domain.update.contracts

Interface IUpdateProcessor

  • All Superinterfaces:
    IBasicObserver, IBasicUpdateProcessor, IBasicUpdateSource, IObserver, IUpdateSource
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    ActionInput, CompositeAction, CompositeActionFly, CompositeActionFlyCatch, ForcedRemiseObserver, GameController, InputProvider, OutOfMovesObserver, UpdateProcessor, UpdatePropagator

    public interface IUpdateProcessor
extends IObserver, IUpdateSource, IBasicUpdateProcessor
    Combines IUpdateSource with IObserver to form an IUpdateProcessor. This interface is typically employed to directly propagate any updates it receives from its observees to its observers. However, any instance that observes updates, processes them and emits them again can use this interface.
